V<div>\u000a<p>While I was home in VA this past week, my mom and I schemed and decided that I should buy a new camera.  I&#8217;ve been wanting to get a DSLR for a while now, and I&#8217;ll actually be able to afford it with my UROP this summer.  So, I purchased a Canon Rebel T1i, which also happened to come with two lenses:  the 18-55mm, and the 55-250mm.  The 18-55mm is not too bad for a starting lens, although I&#8217;d really love to get my hands on a 50mm f/1.8 or f/1.6.  The 55-250mm seems to be a relatively good quality telephoto, so at this point I&#8217;ve pretty much got all my bases covered, until I can afford more expensive glass.</p>\u000a<p>Anyway, the camera arrived on Friday, which also happened to be pika&#8217;s Faculty Dinner (where we invite a bunch of professors to come eat food with us).  I seized the opportunity and spent the night shooting about 16GB of photos.  Here are a few of my favorites!  You can find the rest <a href="http://picasaweb.google.com/jessica.b.hamrick/20100528PikaFacultyDinner">here</a>.</p>\u000a<div class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img title="Kyle and Jess" src="http://lh6.ggpht.com/_JLjHO7vyf-I/TAMPaH8e-9I/AAAAAAAAUbw/cH9kYMAPWC0/IMG_0646.jpg" alt="" width="480" height="336" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Kyle and Jess</p></div>\u000a<div class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img title="Spang Making Pasta" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/_JLjHO7vyf-I/TAMNc9SabaI/AAAAAAAAUdg/gtmxyB874os/s720/IMG_0154.jpg" alt="" width="432" height="383" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Spang Making Pasta</p></div>\u000a<div class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img title="Kyle Has Green Eyes" src="http://lh3.ggpht.com/_JLjHO7vyf-I/TAMN1ugtjqI/AAAAAAAAUgY/4zLNKGpsHNc/s912/IMG_0254.jpg" alt="" width="547" height="365" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Kyle Has Green Eyes</p></div>\u000a<div class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img title="Amusing Conversations" src="http://lh5.ggpht.com/_JLjHO7vyf-I/TAMOrWCkg-I/AAAAAAAAUXc/YTEsViqJCZw/IMG_0526.jpg" alt="" width="480" height="320" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Amusing Conversations</p></div>\u000a<div class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img title="Ian" src="http://lh3.ggpht.com/_JLjHO7vyf-I/TAMPeb8-jZI/AAAAAAAAUcM/k2XyGtFn7YY/s720/IMG_0657.jpg" alt="" width="432" height="366" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Ian</p></div>\u000a</div>
